{"word":"G2690 - καταστρέφω - katastréphō - kat-as-tref'-o - Overthrow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταστρέφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katastréphō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-as-tref'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Overthrow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவிழ்"},{"paragraph":"1. to turn over, turn under"},{"paragraph":"2. to overturn, overthrow, throw down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4762 - στρέφω - stréphō - stref'-o/4762\">G4762</a>; to <i>turn</i> upside <i>down</i>, that is, <i>upset:</i> - overthrow.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1294/1294\">G1294</a>, <a href=\"#/G1994/1994\">G1994</a>, <a href=\"#/G1995/1995\">G1995</a>, <a href=\"#/G2690/2690\">G2690</a>, <a href=\"#/G2692/2692\">G2692</a>, <a href=\"#/G3344/3344\">G3344</a>, <a href=\"#/G390/390\">G390</a>, <a href=\"#/G391/391\">G391</a>, <a href=\"#/G4762/4762\">G4762</a>, <a href=\"#/G654/654\">G654</a>"}]}